title: 171: The Trader Joe's Haul Episode (May '22 Edition)
itunes:title: The Trader Joe's Haul Episode (May '22 Edition)
description: In this episode, Lisa, Mikey & Jamie went through a baker’s dozen’s worth of food finds, like a tasty fruity hard seltzer, peanut butter crispy crunchy cookies, a yummy oat creamer, TJ’s famous Incredisauce, and SO MUCH MORE. Plus, the find of all finds, a new cheesy crunchy snack that is AMAZING! So push play now, and then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the finds mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: We headed back to Trader Joe’s, and we think we found the snack of the year on this edition of Chew The Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
